quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,Doob ker sakhti say khenchnay walon ki qasam
  79,2,Band khol ker chora dyney walon ki qasam
  79,3,Aur terney phirnay walon ki qasam
  79,4,Phir dor ker agy barhnay walon ki qasam
  79,5,Phir kam ki tadbeer kernay walon ki qasam
  79,6,Jis din kanpney wali kanpe gi
  79,7,Us ky bad ik peechy aney wali (peechy peechy) aye gi
  79,8,(buhat se)dil us din dharakty hongy
  79,9,Gin ki nigahen nichi hongien
  79,10,kehty hein ke kiya hum pehli ki si halat ki taraf phir lot aye jaein gay
  79,11,Kiya us waqt jab ke hum bosida hadiyaan hojaein gay
  79,12,Kehty hein ke phir to ye lotna nuksandeh hay
  79,13,(maloom hona chaiey)wo to sirf ik (khufnak)dant hay
  79,14,Kay (jis kay zihar hoty hi )wo ik dam medan mein jama hojaein gay
  79,15,Kiya Musa (aleh e salam)ki khabar tumhein phunchi hay
  79,16,Jabkay unhein unkay rab nay pak medan TUA mein pukara
  79,17,(kay)tum firoon kay pass jao unsay sirkashi ikhtyar kerli hay
  79,18,ussy kaho kay kiya to apnai durstagi or islah chata hy
  79,19,Aur yeh ky mein tujhhy terey Rab ki rah dikhata takay tu (uss say) darnay lagy
  79,20,Pus ussay bari nishani dikhai
  79,21,To us ney jhutlaya aur na fermani ki
  79,22,Phir palta dor dhoop kertay huye
  79,23,Phir sabb ko jama kerty pukaara
  79,24,Tum sab ka rab mein hi hun
  79,25,To(sab say buland o baala)) Allah ney bhi usay aakhrat ky aur duneya ky azab mein giriftaar kerliya
  79,26,Be-shak is mein is shaks kay liye ibrat hy jo daray